Taking XPath for a spin:

- XPath is case sensitive

- It will show all the name that that contains the word 'Tom'
//Name[contains(text(), 'Tom')]

- Select all the phone tags that have type attribute
//phone[@type]

- Select all the phone tags that have type equal to mobile attribute
//phone[@type='mobile']

- Select all the photos of Tea
/items/item[type='Tea']/photo
